## Security

This repo is public. Never write actual values from `~/.env` into any file. Use env var names or `<placeholder>` syntax. Use generic names (alice, bob) not real names. Use `localhost` or `<host>` not real IPs. Hookify rules and gitleaks pre-commit enforce this.

